sequenceDiagram
    participant Admin
    participant AdminWeb
    participant API as DuplicateReportController
    participant DupSvc as DuplicateReportService
    participant PoiSvc as PoiService
    participant Noti as NotificationService
    participant DB
    Admin->>AdminWeb: Mở danh sách duplicate report
    AdminWeb->>API: GET /api/duplicate-report
    API->>DupSvc: GetAllAsync(status=Open)
    DupSvc->>DB: SELECT * FROM DuplicateReports WHERE Status='Open'
    DB-->>DupSvc: reports
    DupSvc-->>API: reports
    API-->>AdminWeb: reports
    Admin->>AdminWeb: Chọn report, xem 2 POI A/B
    Admin->>AdminWeb: Quyết định Merge (giữ A, loại B)
    AdminWeb->>API: POST /api/duplicate-report/{id}/merge {keepId:A, removeId:B}
    API->>DupSvc: MergeAsync(reportId, A, B)
    DupSvc->>DB: BEGIN TRANSACTION
    DupSvc->>DB: UPDATE Audio SET PoiId=A WHERE PoiId=B
    DupSvc->>DB: UPDATE PlaybackLog SET PoiId=A WHERE PoiId=B
    DupSvc->>DB: UPDATE POI SET IsActive=0, MergedIntoId=A WHERE Id=B
    DupSvc->>DB: UPDATE DuplicateReport SET Status='Merged', ResolvedBy=?
    DupSvc->>DB: COMMIT
    DB-->>DupSvc: ok
    DupSvc->>Noti: Notify saler của B: "POI đã được gộp vào A"
    DupSvc-->>API: Success
    API-->>AdminWeb: 200 OK
    AdminWeb-->>Admin: Refresh danh sách
